 mass WIMP may be detectable at the 1-3mK level in the\nfrequency range 55MHz < $\\nu$ < 119MHz corresponding to 11 < z < 25, and at the\n1-10mK level in the frequency range 30MHz < $\\nu$ < 40MHz corresponding to 35 <\nz < 46.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 22 Feb 2013 01:37:43 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 21 Nov 2013 19:30:43 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Fri, 29 Aug 2014 20:58:28 GMT"}],"update_date":"2014-10-02"}
