y breaking in\neither two or three branching singularities is examined. Characteristic\nfeatures are observed when one, two, or three exceptional points are encircled\nsimultaneously.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 22 Feb 2013 15:08:59 GMT"}],"update_date":"2013-07-08"}
